Subject: NEA CU Upgrade
Description: I advised the customer to upgrade NEA to the latest version because the SharePoint Permission scan takes over 15 days and is aborted before completion. The scan used to take between 3 to 5 days to complete.
What_We_Know__c:
The customer is having a performance issue on SharePoint.
It takes over 15 days to scan SPAA (Permission scan)
The customer is on the 11.6.0.11 version
I advise the customer to upgrade to the latest version.
Solution_Comment__c:
We upgraded NEA to the latest version
We upgraded AIC to the newest version
We upgraded Sensitive Data Add-On to the latest version
We upgraded Activity Monitor to the latest version
We upgraded the Proxy to the latest version
